rows.label: qev042205_MSG0001
rows.name: WOOOW wowow! Wow![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0002
rows.name:
Divine Nupopon thrilled to finally meet someone
so strong.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0003
rows.name:
Back when Divine Nupopon first became spirit,
it seemed unlikely any friend would come along
who could beat Divine Nupopon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0004
rows.name: Divine Nopopon sure has eye for talent![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0005
rows.name:
That, and super annoying personality.
But good heart underneath, so try to be patient,
okay, friend?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_JNK0010
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev042205_SEL0011
rows.name:
Promise that you'll try to get along
with the Divine Nopopon.

rows.label: qev042205_JNK0020
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: qev042205_SEL0021
rows.name:
Say that you could never be
friends with a guy like that.

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0006
rows.name: Friend is strong AND mature![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0007
rows.name:
Divine Nupopon is glad friend was the one to clear
trial of spirits.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0008
rows.name: Friend is sure to use power of spirits for good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0009
rows.name:
Any normal person would agree.
And yet, friend is here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0010
rows.name:
If friend wanted nothing to do with Divine Nopopon,
friend could have walked away without accepting trial.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0011
rows.name:
But friend stayed, sat through annoying ramblings,
and made it this far.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0012
rows.name: Few are capable of that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0013
rows.name: All right. Divine Nupopon will bless stone now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0014
rows.name: Nupo...nopo...nupopoPOPOPON![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0015
rows.name: All done.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0016
rows.name: Stay sharp, friend! See this through to end.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0017
rows.name:
...Hmm? Friend is expecting something else?
Go on! Shoo![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0018
rows.name:
Ooh, but tell Divine Nopopon to keep sending more
friends to take trial.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042205_MSG0019
rows.name: Sitting around all day as arenatect gets boring.[ST:wait ]
